	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="">Proc lasts 24 secs</a> <a id="fs8" href="#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
