	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Was over in L Fay tonight hunting for frightling's to try and get a skull (and an earring of course) and got one of these early.&nbsp;&nbsp;Snazzy for lower levels, and I can see a use for a lot of classes, but some just wouldnt need it, or it wouldnt be viable.<br/><br/>BUT...  Imagine a rogue using this, and switching to a superior weapon once it proc'd...  Free back stabs :)  I timed it tonight in EC and the proc lasts 4 pulses (24 secs) so that would give the rogue 2 or 3 backstabs.  Nice for a low lev rogue.<br/><br/>Oh, I was hitting for 25's max that I noticed with it.  Is a novelty item for me, being a bard but an entertaining one.  Allready have a 55 ranger in the area wanting one :)<br/><br/>It proc'd for a 23 druid (regularly btw), so a proc lev of 15 doesnt sound too low.  It dropped for me off an undead sprite horror, so it seems that it can be any undead sprite that drops it.<br/><br/>For those that want one, good luck.  And take into account what it will be replacing.  It IS primary only.</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
